### Youyu - Launch Security Hardening
### These checks are evidence-oriented smoke requests for the launch security task.
### Do not commit real staging domains, JWTs, provider credentials, or local .env files.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@allowedOrigin = http://localhost:5173
@blockedOrigin = https://untrusted.example.test
@userToken = mock-1001-USER
@adminToken = mock-9001-ADMIN

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# CORS
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Allowed local origin preflight - dev/seed/test/default only
OPTIONS {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Origin: {{allowedOrigin}}
Access-Control-Request-Method: GET
Access-Control-Request-Headers: authorization

###

### Untrusted origin preflight - expect no Access-Control-Allow-Origin match
OPTIONS {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Origin: {{blockedOrigin}}
Access-Control-Request-Method: GET
Access-Control-Request-Headers: authorization

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Mock-token boundary
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

###

### Mock token works only in dev/seed/test/default local modes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### Protected user endpoint without token - expect 401 envelope
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/profile

###

### Admin endpoint with user token - expect forbidden envelope
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### Admin endpoint with admin token - dev/seed/test/default local permission smoke
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Payment mock boundary
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

###

### Payment gateway exposure - staging/prod-like profiles must not list mock
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/gateway
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
